  &lt;p id="1qcRM5"&gt;Within 30 minutes of the attempted assassination of former President Donald Trump, Elon &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/13/24198049/trump-x-shooting-conspiracy-theories-trending"&gt;Musk did what he had previously promised not to do&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="nNw6UV"&gt;“I fully endorse President Trump and hope for his rapid recovery,” the billionaire posted on X. So much for that vow to stay on the sidelines. &lt;/p&gt;
